main event: Two objects were observed in the sky over Grand Canyon National Park on 23 August 1965.
interesting points: The objects appeared from the West, with a larger or brighter object leading the smaller one,The sighting lasted for approximately 4 minutes,The objects disappeared into the brightness of the dawn,The Air Force suggested that the sighting could have been space debris or high-flying aircraft,The report was part of Project Blue Book, which investigated UFO sightings from 1952 to 1969.
location: Grand Canyon National Park, Arizona, USA
